---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("August 31 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Signs to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service"
  description={isPublished ? "Full Article: Signs It's Time to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service" : "Coming Soon: Signs It's Time to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service"}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Signs It's Time to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service"
    description="Are you settling for subpar cleaning? Learn the undeniable signs that it is time to fire your current cleaning service and upgrade to reliable professionals."
    publishDate="August 31 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Comparison/Direct Response
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Signs It's Time to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming August 31 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>August 31 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>Is It Time to Fire Your Current Cleaning Service in The Shoals?</h2>
<p><strong>If your cleaning service isn't meeting your standards, it may be time to make a change. In The Shoals & Surrounding Areas, you deserve a cleaning team that delivers precision, reliability, and transparency. Here's how to recognize when it's time to move on and invest in a service that respects your home and time.</strong></p>

<h3>1. Inconsistent Quality</h3>
<p>Your home deserves a consistent level of cleanliness. If you've noticed that the quality of cleaning varies from visit to visit, it's a red flag. A premium service should deliver the same meticulous results every time, not just occasionally.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Missed Spots:</strong> Are baseboards, corners, or other areas frequently overlooked?</li>
  <li><strong>Unmet Standards:</strong> Does dust reappear soon after a cleaning session?</li>
</ul>
<p>These inconsistencies suggest a lack of standard operating procedures (SOPs), something that a professional team like The Valley Clean Team guarantees.</p>

<h3>2. Lack of Accountability</h3>
<p>A trustworthy cleaning service acknowledges mistakes and corrects them promptly. If your current provider makes excuses instead of taking ownership, it might be time to reconsider.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>No Follow-Up:</strong> Do they fail to check in on your satisfaction after a job?</li>
  <li><strong>Blame-Shifting:</strong> Do they deflect responsibility for issues?</li>
</ul>
<p>Veteran-owned services, like ours, prioritize integrity and accountability, ensuring your satisfaction is our mission.</p>

<h3>3. Unclear Pricing</h3>
<p>Transparency in pricing is non-negotiable. If your current service hides costs or frequently alters pricing without clear explanations, it's a sign of poor business practice.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Hidden Fees:</strong> Are you surprised by additional charges?</li>
  <li><strong>Inconsistent Quotes:</strong> Do prices change with no rationale?</li>
</ul>
<p>At The Valley Clean Team, we offer upfront, transparent pricing starting at $125, so you always know what to expect.</p>

<h3>4. Poor Communication</h3>
<p>Communication is key to any successful service relationship. If your cleaning team is hard to reach or slow to respond, your time and peace of mind are being compromised.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Delayed Responses:</strong> Is it difficult to get timely feedback or answers?</li>
  <li><strong>Lack of Updates:</strong> Are you left in the dark about schedule changes or issues?</li>
</ul>
<p>Our team ensures clear and direct communication, respecting your time and needs.</p>

<h3>5. Lack of Trust</h3>
<p>Your home is your sanctuary; you should trust those who enter it. If you have doubts about the integrity or professionalism of your current cleaners, it's a significant concern.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Vetting Issues:</strong> Are the cleaners not thoroughly vetted?</li>
  <li><strong>Unprofessional Behavior:</strong> Have there been incidents of rudeness or negligence?</li>
</ul>
<p>The Valley Clean Team is comprised of vetted specialists who follow strict military-precision checklists, ensuring trust and reliability.</p>

<h3>6. No Guarantees</h3>
<p>A reliable service should stand behind its work with a satisfaction guarantee. If your current provider does not offer this, it may be time to find one that does.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>No Satisfaction Guarantee:</strong> Are you left dissatisfied with no recourse?</li>
  <li><strong>Lack of Reassurance:</strong> Are you uneasy about the service outcome?</li>
</ul>
<p>We guarantee a perfect clean every time, delivering peace of mind and exceptional results.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time with The Valley Clean Team</h3>
<p>Don't settle for less than excellence. If any of these signs resonate with you, it's time to make a change. The Valley Clean Team offers premium, systematic cleaning with transparency and accountability. Book your free quote today and experience a guaranteed clean that respects your home and time. Reclaim your weekend—schedule your service now!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">August 31 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
